</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/ec7200acd984a1d3a3d7dc455e262fbe54f7f6e0" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.636ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle T}"=
></span> is not 0, or (ii) the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Var=
iance" title=3D"Variance">variance</a> of <span class=3D"mwe-math-element m=
we-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-math=
