=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P-value#cite_note-11"><span class=3D"cite=
-bracket">[</span>9<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>=20
</p><p>Different <i>p</i>-values based on independent sets of data can be c=
ombined, for instance using <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fisher=
%27s_combined_probability_test" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Fisher's com=
bined probability test">Fisher's combined probability test</a>.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Distribution">Distribution<=
/h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[=
</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DP-value&amp;=
action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D5" title=3D"Edit section: Distribution"><span>e=
